## Welcome to Safe Storage (ss-cli) project pages

**What is ss-cli?**

Console application for storing passwords. It is part of bachelor thesis called Systems for storing authentication data.


**Authors and Contributors**

2012, Radek Jirovský (@rjirovsky)

Having trouble with Pages? Check out the documentation at http://help.github.com/pages or contact support@github.com and we’ll help you sort it out.
